text: "Giants" is a song by Dermot Kennedy, a musician and singer-songwriter from the Republic of Ireland. It was released on the 24 June 2020 by Riggins, Interscope and Island. The song was written by Stephen Kozmeniuk, Scott Harris and Kennedy himself and peaked at number one on the Irish Singles Chart. In an interview, Kennedy said that it is a song he'd had for a while before it was released. Category:2020 songs
title: Giants (Dermot Kennedy song)
